'Yan sanda shida sun ji rauni a cikin tashin hankali da ya barke a gidan yarin maza na tsaro, a cewar sanarwar da hukumar kula da tsare-tsaren ta bayar.
Rikicin ya barke a gidan yarin Her Majesty's Long Latin a Worcestershire da misalin karfe 9:30 na safe na ranar Lahadi kuma har yanzu yana ci gaba.
An tura rundunar 'yan sanda na musamman don magance rikicin da ya shafi fursunoni takwas da suka faru a wani bangare.
An kwantar da jami'an 'yan sanda da kananan raunin fuska a lokacin rikicin.
Wani mai magana da yawun kurkuku ya ce: "Ma'aikatan da aka horar musamman sun ɗauki nauyin magance abin da ya faru a kurkukun mai girma Long Latin.
An kwantar da ma'aikatan jirgin shida da suka ji rauni.
