"Ba na bukatar yin gasa a wannan lokaci na aikina don in shirya", in ji shi.
Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara jerin tarurruka da suka fara a garin Wheeling da ke jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya haɗa da ziyarar zuwa yankunan da ke kusa da juna, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake ana jiran amincewar da za a yi masa a kotun koli, Trump na neman karfafa goyon bayan jama'a a zaben da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar asarar iko a majalisa a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia za a yi kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon taron a kan layi?
Taron Trump a garin Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a karfe 7 na dare, Satumba, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump na iya yin magana game da sauraron sauraron dan takarar kotun koli na wannan makon, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya faru ne a cikin yanayi mai matukar damuwa saboda zargin aikata laifuka na jima'i, tare da kuri'ar tabbatar da majalisar dattawa da aka dakatar har tsawon mako guda yayin da ake ci gaba da binciken FBI.
Amma, babban manufar wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar rashin daidaito a zaben na watan Nuwamba don samun damar yin aiki.
Kamar yadda rahotanni suka nuna, shugaban kasar Trump ya ce, taron da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, zai taimaka wa 'yan adawa da masu goyon baya su yi aiki tare, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da na wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a majalisa na da muhimmanci sosai a ajandar shugaban kasa, wanda shugaban ya ke tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama yayin da muke cikin lokacin kamfen", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron da aka shirya a daren yau a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan nan zuwa jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar 'yan Republican a West Virginia don Majalisar Dattawa, wanda ke da kasa a cikin kuri'un.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi wani mataki a kan kuri'un zabe ba", in ji Simon Hender, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA na da ƙarfin gwiwa don yin wasa da fatan ci gaba da rayuwa yayin da take tafiya zuwa wasannin zakara na ranar Lahadi
Bayan wasanni uku na wasa guda, wasan hudu na ranar Asabar da yamma, wataƙila shi ne abin da gasar Ryder Cup take bukata.
Dandalin da ke motsawa a cikin motsa jiki abu ne da aka yi da shi, amma 'yan wasa suna gaskata da shi sosai, musamman ma a irin wannan wasa.
A ina ne za su ce akwai ƙarfin hali a yanzu?
"Ya kasance maki shida a gaba, kuma yanzu yana da maki hudu a gaba, don haka wataƙila muna da ɗan ƙaramin ƙarfi", in ji Jordan Speith yayin da yake barin rana.
A gaskiya, Turai tana da fa'ida ta hanyar samun maki huɗu a gaba da kuma sauran maki 12.
Amirkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna da iska a cikin jirgin ruwa, kuma suna da abubuwa da yawa da za su ƙarfafa su, kamar su Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare a dukan yini, kuma kowannensu ya sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya yi kisa daga tee a kan green kuma ya kafa misali.
Muryar murna ta kara karfi yayin da ya ci gaba da zagaye, yana yin wani muhimmin tasiri don samun wasan hudu duk-square lokacin da shi da Thomas suka sauka biyu bayan biyu.
Wasan da suka yi na lashe wasan a ranar 15 ga watan da ya gabata ya zo ne da irin wannan murnar da ke nuna imaninsa cewa tawagar Amurka ba ta fice ba.
"Ya kamata ka duba cikin zuciyarka kuma ka damu da wasan da kake yi", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da kowane ɗan wasa ya bar.
Rami 18 don rubuta tarihi.
'Yan wasa guda biyu da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da babu wanda ya ce.
Ƙwararrun 'yan'uwa biyu na Turai sun yi nasara a hudu daga cikin hudu kuma suna ganin ba su da wani abu da ba daidai ba.
"Mollywood" ita ce kawai tagwayen da ba ta buga bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma kuma ta kauce wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, da yammacin Juma'a da kuma tara a ranar Juma'a.
Wannan wasa, da kuma yadda ake ganin ana samun kuzari daga wajen masu kallo, ya tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su yi nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari shahara wajen lashe gasar Turai yayin da rana ta sauka a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau a yi duka a lokaci guda a cikin ramuka daban-daban.
Tattaunawa game da ɗaukakar Turai har yanzu bai kai lokaci ba.
Baba Watson da Web Simpson sun saka wa Sergio Garcia, jarumin wasan kwallon kafa na safe, tabarau lokacin da ya yi wasa tare da Alex Noren.
Da bogey da biyu biyu a gaban tara suka jefa Mutanen Espanya da Swede cikin rami sosai har ba za su iya fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, ba wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin ramin da kake ciki.
Wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu suna da ban sha'awa sosai a kallon su daga nesa saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba sa bayarwa, da kuma yadda dabarun za su iya canzawa a wani lokaci.
Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin tawagar ta zuwa yanzu kuma tana da gagarumar nasara a ranar karshe, amma wannan wasa na hudu ya kuma nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da ƙarfin hali, duk da shakkun wasu.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai za ta yi nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan ta yi nasara a wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu a ranar Asabar da ci 10-6 a kan Amurka.
'Yan wasan biyu masu ban sha'awa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun shiga tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods mai fafatawa kuma sun sami damar jagoranci a Le Golf National har zuwa yanzu a cikin maki huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wadda ke ƙoƙarin riƙe kofin da ta yi hasara a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka wuce, ta mamaye ƙungiyar Amurka da ta yi rashin nasara a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, da ci 3-1.
Amurka ta fi tsayayya da wasan hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rufe bambancin ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na wasan tseren a ranar Lahadi domin ya rike kofin.
Fleetwood shine dan wasan Turai na farko da ya lashe maki hudu a wasan, yayin da tare da Molinari, wanda aka fi sani da "Mollywood", bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, sun kasance kawai na biyu da suka lashe maki hudu a wasanni hudu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reid a wasan kwallon kafa, sai suka hada karfi don su doke Woods da dan Amurka mai suna Bryson Desambo a wasan kwallon kafa mai suna 5&4.
Woods, wanda ya yi kasala a wasannin biyu na ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu fitattun abubuwa, amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasansa 29 a wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu da kuma na bakwai.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta don wasan kwallon hudu na safe, ya koma abokin wasan Henry Stenson don wasan hudu tare da 2 & 1 da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Keppa suka ci, suna samun matsayi na farko da na uku a cikin jerin duniya.
Ba komai ya tafi daidai ba a Turai, sai dai ranar farin ciki, mai sanyi a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Dan wasan kasar sau uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa wa 'yan wasan Amurkawa maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci nasara 2&1 mai wahala akan John Rum da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin wasan kwallon kafa kuma sun dawo daga baya don kayar da Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a wasan kwallon kafa yayin da suka rasa ramuka biyu a farkon.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup wata tawagar ta iya murmurewa yayin da ta yi asara da maki hudu a wasan guda, ko da yake saboda shi ne mai lashe gasar, Furyk ya isa ya ci nasara don riƙe kofin.
Amma, bayan sun kasance a matsayi na biyu na tsawon kwanaki biyu, ya zama kamar ba za su iya yin yaƙi a ranar Lahadi ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makaman ba tare da amincewa da juna ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake ci gaba da kakabawa Amurka ya kara tsananta masa, kuma kasarsa ba za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta ba a karkashin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar ta duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu kyau" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin nukiliya da na makamai masu linzami, cire wuraren gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani irin martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba za a sami amincewa da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a karkashin irin wannan yanayi babu wata hanyar da za mu iya fara kawar da makamanmu".
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafe-korafen Koriya ta Arewa game da kin amincewar Washington kan yiwuwar "matakan" na kawar da makaman nukiliya, wanda zai ba Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da take ci gaba da aiwatar da aikin, sanarwar tasa ta kasance mai mahimmanci cewa bai yi watsi da kawar da makaman nukiliya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ya yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da sanarwar da Kim Jong-un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai ci da kuma shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "rashin makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya ta Kudu", yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin samar da tabbacin tsaro ga Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na neman kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta "sallama" makaman nukiliyarta da farko.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kiran sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa da aka dora wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan 'farkon' kawar da makaman nukiliya, kuma tana kara matsin lamba ta hanyar barazanar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar yin barazanar, har ma da hana 'karshen yakin' ", in ji Ri.
"Hankalin cewa takunkumi na iya sa mu durƙusa mafarki ne na waɗanda ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumi na ci gaba da ƙara sa mu cikin rashin amincewa".
Ri bai yi wani bayani ba game da wani taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump, wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi nuni da shi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Ministan, duk da haka, ya yi nuni da tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: "Idan abokin tarayya a batun kare makaman nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, to kare makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya ba zai kai ga irin wannan rashin mafita ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bambam da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya fada wa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da aka kai wa Amurka da makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa ba makawa ne saboda "Shugaba Kishi" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin makami mai linzami" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim don ƙarfin zuciyarsa na ci gaba da matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran abin da za a yi kuma cewa takunkumin ya kamata ya kasance har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi hakan, yana cewa "Idan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar, ba matsala".
China da Rasha sun ce ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Amma, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi a kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da himma da kuma ci gaba har sai an cimma cikakkiyar, karshe da kuma tabbatar da kare makaman nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro ya amince da takunkumin da aka kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 a kokarin da ake yi na hana tallafawa shirin nukiliya da makamin harin ballistic na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta yi kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, sai dai Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi sa'o'i kadan bayan haka da cewa yana da "bukatun 'yan bindiga".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a ganawarta da Moon a wannan watan ta lalata wata tashar makamai masu linzami da kuma wata cibiyar nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
Ya bayyana cewa Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema su ne tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi wa Singapore alkawari da kuma inganta daidaita dangantakar da ke tsakanin kasar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna halartar darussa game da yadda za su samu isasshen hutu
A wannan shekara, wani sabon bincike a Jami'ar Harvard ya nemi dukan daliban jami'a su yi barci sosai a ƙoƙarin da suke yi na yaƙi da al'adar yin karatu dare da rana da kuma yawan shan maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a jami'a mafi girma a duniya sau da yawa ba su san ainihin abubuwa ba, kamar yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles T. Chiesler, Farfesa a Harkokin Magunguna na Harvard Medical School da kuma likita a asibitin Brigham and Women's, ya tsara darasin, wanda ya yi imanin shi ne na farko a cikin Amurka.
Ta samu kwarin gwiwa ta fara wannan darasi ne bayan ta yi jawabi game da yadda rashin barci yake shafar ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshe, wata yarinya ta zo ta ce, "Me ya sa na koyi wannan ne a shekarar karshe?"
Ta ce ba a taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci ba - abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji ta a jaridar The Telegraph.
Darasi, wanda aka fara a wannan shekara, yana koya wa ɗalibai muhimman ƙa'idodi game da yadda halayen barci mai kyau ke taimakawa wajen samun nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyar jiki.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma shugaban jami'ar na kula da lafiyar jama'a, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar hada wannan darasi ne bayan da aka gano cewa dalibai suna rashin bacci a cikin mako sosai.
Darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A cikin wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai suke danna kofi, labule, takalma, da littattafai don su sami bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma muhimmancin yin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, mahalarta sun koyi yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar da ke ɗauke da gumaka masu ma'ana, ta ƙarfafa masu halarta su yi tunani game da rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba zai canja halin ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da hakkin su sani, kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san sakamakon shan sigari a kan lafiyarku", in ji Farfesa Chiessler.
Al'adar alfahari da yin karatu dare da rana har yanzu tana nan, in ji shi, ya daɗa cewa fasaha ta zamani da kuma matsin lamba a kan ɗalibai na nufin cewa rashin barci matsala ce da ke ƙaruwa.
Ya ce samun isasshen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na dalibai wajen magance damuwa, gajiya, da kuma damuwa, har ma don guje wa samun nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta yi yunwa, kuma hakan yana sa a ji yunwa.
Raymond Shaw, ɗan shekara 19 da ke California da ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da kuma ilimin halittu, ya taimaki Farfesa Chiesler wajen tsara darasin, ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce darasin ya sa ya yi wa'azi sosai kuma ya sa ya soma neman darasi a ko'ina a makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, ya yi fata, shi ne ya bukaci dukan ɗaliban digiri su halarci irin wannan shirin kafin su fara karatu a wannan ma'aikatar ilimi mai tsananin gasa.
Farfesa Chiesler ya shawarci ɗalibai su kafa faɗakarwa game da lokacin barci da kuma lokacin farkawa, kuma su san cewa "haske mai-fitarwa" da ake samu daga allon lantarki da kuma hasken LED zai iya sa jijiyoyin jiki su yi sanyi, kuma hakan zai iya sa su soma rashin barci.
Livingston zuwa Rangers 1-0 Menga ya ci wa 'yan Gerard kwallo
Rangers sun sha wahala a wani mummunan rauni a waje, kamar yadda harbi da Dolly Menga ya yi ya jagoranci Stephen Gerrard na gefe zuwa 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Iberbrooks na neman cin nasarar farko a waje tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da suka yi a St. Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta yi rashin nasarar Gerard na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, wanda ya bar kungiyar maki takwas a baya da Hurts, wanda ke kan gaba a cikin rukunin Ladbrokes.
Menga ya buga da minti bakwai kafin a kammala wasan kuma Rangers din da suka yi rashin nasara sun kasa mayar da martani.
Yayin da Rangers suka sauka a matsayi na shida, Livingston ta hau zuwa na uku, da ci daya kawai daga Hibernian da ke gaba.
Kuma wasu matsaloli na iya jiran Rangers, kamar yadda mai kula da Calum Spence ya bukaci a dauki taimakon gaggawa don rauni a kan kai wanda aka yi masa ta hanyar wani abu da aka jefa daga kan tudu.
Gerard ya yi sau takwas a cikin tawagar kuma ya ci Air a wasan kusa da na Betfred Cup.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya tafi da wannan rukunin "Livi 11" wanda ya sami maki daga Hartz a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda wannan injin mai mai daɗi ya iya murkushe duk wani ƙoƙari na abokan hamayyarsa.
Rangers sun fi kowa a wurin, amma Livingston ya fi kowa a wurin.
Ya kamata ya ci kwallo a minti na biyu, lokacin da Menga ya fara zura kwallo ya tura Scott Pittman cikin yankin Alan McGregor, amma dan wasan tsakiya bai samu kwallon ba.
Wasan da Keegan Jacobs ya yi ya kai ga Craig Halkett, amma dan wasansa Alan Lithgow ya yi nasara wajen fitar da kwallon daga raga.
Rangers sun ci gaba da rike ragamar, amma da alama akwai bege fiye da imani a wasan a cikin na karshe.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi imanin cewa ya kamata ya ci kwallo a 15' yayin da ya yi karo da Stephen Lawless, amma mai wasan kwallon kafa Stephen Thompson ya yi watsi da korafin dan wasan na Colombia.
Rangers sun yi harbi biyu ne kawai a cikin rabin farko, amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ambrose Liam Kelly bai damu ba game da Lasagna Coulibaly da Ovie Ezzaria.
Ko da yake a cikin minti 34 na farko na wasan Livy ya kasance a fili a ƙasa da tsammanin, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa ya cancanci nasara don ƙoƙari kawai.
Har ila yau, Rangers sun kasa magance matsalar Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai yi wani abu ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe kansa kuma ya sami Menga wanda kawai ya kammala ƙoƙari.
Gerard ya yi canje-canje a rabin lokaci ya cire Coulibaly ya sa Ryan Kent, canjin ya yi tasiri kusan nan take, yayin da mai tsaron ya ba Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya gudu daga layinsa don toshe shi.
