Shafi daga littafinmu na Sunday Morning: 30 ga Satumba, 1882: kamar yau, shekaru 136 da suka shige, wato ranar da aka haifi Johann Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger, masanin lissafi a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, wannan abu ne da ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga lokacin, an yi amfani da na'urar lissafin Geiger a al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda aka nuna a fim din Bells of Coronado na shekara ta 1950, wanda ya ƙunshi masana kimiyya Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar ne da ake amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu guba kamar uranium.
Sa'ad da ka saka waɗannan na'urorin, za ka ji yadda abubuwa suke aiki a kan ƙarfe".
Evans: "Duba, yana yin kamar mahaukaci!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Duk da haka, ƙirar da ke ɗauke da sunansa tana ci gaba da aikinta.
