Kanye West ya kare Trump, yana saka hat da ke dauke da kalmar MAGA, bayan ya fito a SNL.
Ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Kanye West ya yi watsi da shi a cikin studio a lokacin wani taron Satumba da Daren Rayuwa bayan wata hira ta waje da ya yaba wa Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai tsaya takara a zaben 2020.
Bayan ya gabatar da waƙarsa ta uku don maraice, mai taken Ghost Town, inda ya sa hat na baseball tare da taken Make America Great Again, ya ba da wasan kwaikwayo na rashin amincewa da Democrats kuma ya sake ba da goyon bayansa ga Trump.
"Na sha yin magana da wani farin mutum, sai ya ce, "To, me kake so game da Trump?
"Idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amirka tun da daɗewa", in ji ta.
SNL ta bude da wani shirin fim mai suna Matt Damon, wanda ya nuna yadda wani tauraron fim din Hollywood, Brett Kavanaugh ya gabatar da shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa game da zargin da Kristin Blazy Ford ta yi na cin zarafin mata.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, an wallafa bidiyon da ke nuna yadda West ya kamu da cutar ta hanyar sada zumunta ta hanyar Chris Rock.
Ba a san ko Rock ya yi ƙoƙari ya yi wa West ba'a da wannan sakon.
West ya kuma yi korafi ga masu sauraro cewa ba a kula da shi ba a baya bayan fage saboda hatinsa.
"An yi mini wasan ƙwallon ƙafa a bayan fage.
Suka ce, "Kada ka fita da hat".
An yi mini wasan bowling!
Kuma suna cewa ban san abin da ke faruwa da ni ba", in ji shi, a cewar Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba da cewa, "Ban san abin da ke faruwa da ni ba. Zan sa mayafin Superman, domin ba wanda zai iya gaya mini abin da zan yi.
Ku gwada ƙauna".
An yi watsi da maganganunsa a kalla sau biyu daga masu sauraro kuma SNL ta bayyana cewa tana cikin mawuyacin hali, Variety ta ruwaito, tare da wani mutum ya shaida wa mujallar: "A cikin dukan ɗakin studio akwai shiru".
An gayyaci West a matsayin maye gurbin dan wasan kwaikwayo Ariana Grande, wanda tsohon saurayinta, dan wasan rapper Mac Miller, ya mutu 'yan kwanaki da suka gabata.
West ya rikita wasu mutane lokacin da ya rera I Love It a matsayin Perrier.
Wanda ke jagorantar kungiyar TPUSA mai ra'ayin mazan jiya, Candace Turner, ta goyi bayan West, ta wallafa a shafin Twitter cewa: "Ga daya daga cikin mafiya karfin zuciya: Godiya ga wadanda suka yi tsayayya da wannan zanga-zanga".
