Tauraruwar Game of Thrones, Kit Harrington, ta yi tir da cutar da ke sa namiji ya zama mai guba
Kit Harrington ya shahara sosai saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin John Snow a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO na Game of Thrones.
Amma kuma, dan wasan, mai shekara 31, ya soki halin jarumin, yana mai cewa irin wadannan wasannin da ake yi a talabijin suna gaya wa yara maza cewa dole ne su yi aiki tuƙuru don su sami daraja.
Da yake magana da mujallar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce "wani abu ba daidai ba ne" kuma ya yi mamakin yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa ta maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasansa ta Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, ma mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana da "ra'ayi mai karfi" game da batun.
"Ni kaina, yanzu, na yi imani da hakan. A ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji?" in ji ta.
"Me muke koya wa maza yayin da suke girma game da matsalar da muke fuskanta yanzu?"
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na haɓaka ƙwayoyin cuta na maza saboda halayen maza da yake tallatawa.
Ta ci gaba: "Mecece dabi'a, kuma menene aka koya?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin da kuma a kan titi da ke sa samari su ji cewa dole ne su nuna irin wannan halin domin su zama maza?
Ina tsammanin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya ta zamaninmu. Ta yaya za mu canza wannan?
Babu shakka, akwai wani abu da ya faru da matasanmu".
A cikin hirar ya kuma yarda cewa ba ya shirin yin wani prequel ko sequel na Game of Thrones, bayan ƙarshen jerin a bazara mai zuwa, yana cewa "karshen fadace-fadace da dawakai".
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai taka rawa a wani sabon fim na Sam Shepard mai suna True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai samar da fina-finai da ɗan'uwansa, wanda shi ma ɗan fashi ne.
Aikin da ya yi kwanan nan ya bayyana cewa saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya samu daga Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata a kan wasan kwaikwayon, don haka ta ba ni wata hanyar da za ta ba ni iyalina na gaba da rayuwata daga yanzu", in ji shi.
Rose ta taka rawar Hegrit, mai son John Snow, wanda Kit ya taka rawa, a cikin kyautar Emmy.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie na Scotland.
HIV/Aids: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar kashi 14 cikin ɗari na sababbin cututtuka
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan 'yan kasarta da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
A ƙasar, fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suke fama da cutar, in ji hukumar kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai an bayar da rahoton sabbin mutane 40,000.
A cikin yawancin, an yaɗa sababbin cututtuka ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga abin da ya faru a dā.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin saboda jinin da ke dauke da cutar.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya kusan ragu, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka bayyana a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma idan aka kwatanta da shekarar da ta shige, adadin mutanen da suke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i ta zama babban batu ga al'ummar Lakota a kasar Sin.
An yi wa luwadi yancin kisa a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga al'ummar LGBT ya kasance ruwan dare gama gari.
Domin ra'ayoyin da suka dace na ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtukan da ake yadawa suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magungunan cutar HIV ga kowa, a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani jami'in gwamnati ya leaked bayanan 'yan majalisar wakilai na Republican, ta yi Allah wadai da "karya mai hadari" da kuma "ra'ayin makirci"
A ranar Asabar, wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar wakilai uku a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yar majalisar Democrat ta Los Angeles ta yi ikirarin cewa masu sharhi da shafukan yanar gizo na "dama" ne ke tallata zargin.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da kuma ƙarin munanan ƙarya", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
An ce bayanan da aka fitar sun hada da adireshin gida da lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattawa Lindsay Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orin Harts na Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a Intanet a ranar Alhamis kuma an bayyana cewa an buga su ne ta hanyar wani mutum da ba a san shi ba daga cikin mahalli na Capitol Hill a lokacin sauraron kwamitin majalisar dattawa game da zargin aikata laifuka na jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
An samu wannan bayanan ne bayan da 'yan majalisar suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ruwaito cewa adireshin IP da ke gano tushen aika sakonnin ya danganta da ofishin Waters kuma sun wallafa bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, The Hill ta ruwaito.
"Wannan da'awar da babu tushe ba ta da gaskiya kuma karya ce", in ji Waters.
"Majalisarmu ta ce, ba za a iya cewa, mutumin da aka yi wa sata ba, wanda aka yi wa sata, da kuma wanda aka yi wa sata, saboda wannan yaudara da kuma ƙarya da aka yi, shi ne ya sa aka yi wa sata.
Wannan da'awar ba ta da tushe kuma ƙarya ce ta karya".
Sanarwar Waters ta samu zargi a yanar gizo, ciki har da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House, Ari Fleisher.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana cike da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da ƙarfin zama dan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Bai kamata ya zama abin kunya ba.
Bai kamata ya yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa ya yi zarginsa ba.
Ya kamata ya kasance mai natsuwa da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleisher ya bayyana cewa yana kwatanta yadda Waters ta amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukarsa suka zarge shi da cewa ya yi fushi sosai a zaman kotun na ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman tsige Waters a zaben da za a yi tsakanin 'yan takara, ya bayyana tunaninsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Babban abu ne idan gaskiya ne", in ji ta a shafinta na Twitter.
A cikin sanarwar ta, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya sanar da "hukumomi da hukumomin da suka dace game da waɗannan zarge-zargen".
"Za mu yi iyakar ƙoƙarinmu mu samu waɗanda suka yi wannan", ya ci gaba, "da kuma sa su ba da lissafi ga dukan ayyukansu da suke da lahani da kuma haɗari ga kowa da kuma dukan ma'aikatanmu".
Fim din Johnny English ya Sake Buga - wani fim din leken asiri mai suna Rowan Atkinson
An riga an yi al'ada a bincika alamun Brexit a kowane sabon fim na Burtaniya kuma wannan ya zama gaskiya a wannan farfadowar fim ɗin na wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake dawowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English: The Return.
Shin wannan abin dariya game da yadda muke da rashin lafiya zai iya zama sabon damar fitar da kayayyaki ga al'ummarmu?
A kowane hali, Johnny Inglis da ba shi da ƙwarewa da idanu ya sami damar sabunta lasisinsa na yin fim na biyu. sunansa ya nuna cewa yana da wani abu mai ban dariya wanda aka tsara don masu kallo na ba-Ingilishi.
Wannan, hakika, wani dan leken asiri ne mai tsananin son zuciya wanda, yayin da yake nuna cewa yana da kyan gani da kuma dabi'un wani dan leken asiri, yana kawo wani abu zuwa ga Clouseau, tare da wani abu na "Mista Bean" da kuma wani abu daga mutumin da ya buga waƙa guda ɗaya a cikin waƙar fim din "The Road to Fire" a lokacin bikin bude gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Har ila yau, ya dogara ne akan matafiyi da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin fim a cikin tallan TV da aka manta da shi na Barclaycard, yana lalata rikici a hanyarsa.
Akwai wani abu ko biyu masu kyau a cikin wannan fim na JE na ƙarshe.
Na ji daɗi sa'ad da Johnny Inglis ya kusanci wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da ya saka makamai na dā kuma allon ya buga kan kwalkwali.
Atkinson yana nuna kwarewarsa a wasan kwaikwayo, duk da haka, wasan kwaikwayo yana da ɗan gajeren lokaci kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman ma a lokacin da "mai tsanani" fim din kamar 007 da Dangerous Mission yanzu sun haɗa da abubuwa masu ban dariya.
Abin dariya kamar yana magana ne ga yara ba manya ba, kuma a ganina, waƙar Johnny English ba ta da ma'ana da kuma dacewa kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim ɗin fim ɗin Binn.
Maganar da ta kasance a kullum ita ce, Birtaniya na cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani babban asirin yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya, ya fallasa duk wani jami'in Birtaniya da ke aikin sa, abin takaici ga jami'in da ke aikin sa, wanda Kevin Eldon ya buga a wani rawar da ba shi da yawa.
Wannan shi ne karshe ga wani firaminista mai girman kai da kuma burin da ke kan iyakar rushewa saboda rashin amincewar siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin mafi kyau da wannan hali wanda ya tuna da Theresa May, amma rubutun ba ya taimaka mata sosai.
Masu ba da shawara a kan harkokin yawon bude ido sun gaya mata cewa, tun da an gano duk wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki, za ta dawo da wani da ba shi da makamai.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny Inglis, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin darektan wata babbar makaranta, amma yana koyar da darussan da ba na hukuma ba ga jami'an leken asiri: a nan akwai wasu kyawawan wurare, kamar yadda Inglis ke ba da makarantar leken asiri kamar makarantar Rock.
Inglis ya koma Whitehall don gaggawa kuma ya sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikin Buff, wanda Ben Miller ya sake yin wasa.
Yanzu, Buff ya auri kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani aiki mai ban mamaki da Vicky Pepperdine ba ta da amfani sosai.
Sai Batman da Robin na sashen Sirrin Mai Martaba suka koma aiki, suka sadu da Ofelia Buletova mai ban mamaki da Olga Kirilenko ta yi.
