Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "tsoratar da jama'a" ta hanyar "tallace-tallace na farfaganda".
Mako guda bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke yada fa'idodin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labarai na Amurka don yada farfagandar ta.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba a kan wani labarin da aka biya na China Daily da ya fito a Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da neman shiga cikin zaben majalisar dattawa a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing ta yi kokarin shiga cikin zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne na wani yunkuri da Washington ta kaddamar domin matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake ba a hana gwamnatocin kasashen waje buga tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwancin su ba, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci mai tsanani kuma sun sanya wa juna wasu haraji kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su.
Sakamakon da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya ya yi niyyar cutar da masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da na Amurka.
Terry Brandt, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, wanda babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona ne ga kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni illa.
Kamar yadda Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wata muhawara a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, "China tana yin irin wannan barazanar ta wajen buga tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"A ƙoƙarin yaɗa wannan farfagandar, gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adun 'yancin magana da kuma 'yancin 'yan jarida na Amirka ta wajen buga talla a kan kuɗin da ake biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Brandstad.
"A akasin haka, a cikin rumfunan Beijing, za ku sami 'yan muryoyi masu banbanci da kuma wakilci na gaskiya game da ra'ayoyi daban-daban da jama'ar kasar Sin ke da su game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, tunda kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa "ɗaya daga cikin manyan jaridu a China ta ki amincewa da tayin buga" labarin nasa, ko da yake bai bayyana ko wane ne ba.
'Yan Republican sun hana mata masu jefa kuri'a yin zabe a lokacin zaben na tsakiyar shekara saboda matsalar da ke tsakanin su da Kavanaugh, manazarta sun yi gargadin hakan
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican ke ci gaba da kare dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh duk da zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a samu adawa, musamman daga mata, a zaben da ke tafe.
Tunanin game da wannan batun ya yi tsami sosai kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun ce suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Ba za a iya gyara waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reer, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, game da wani talifi da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reer ya yi shakkar cewa matakin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya dauka na minti na karshe na neman a binciki lamarin da FBI zai isa ya jawo hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi gobe ba, kuma ba za su manta da shi ba a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karin Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zanga sun yi ta ihu suna cewa "Nuwamba tana zuwa!" a cikin harabar majalisar dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka ba da izinin takarar Kavanaugh, duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blazy Ford, Mic ta ruwaito.
"Jinjina kai da himmar 'yan Democrat za su kai matakin da ba a taɓa gani ba", in ji Stu Rodenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa, a shafin yanar gizon.
"Suna cewa ya riga ya yi yawa, kuma gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman a cikin rukunin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin birane da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 waɗanda, yayin da suke ƙin shugaban ƙasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a".
Tun kafin Ford ta bayyana a fili inda ta bayyana dalla-dalla zargin cin zarafin da ta yi wa dan takarar kotun koli, manazarta sun yi hasashen cewa za a iya samun koma baya idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da zaben.
"Babban rikici ne ga Jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun jefa kuri'a a kwamitin ba ne ko kuma game da kuri'ar karshe ko kuma ko za a fitar da Kavanaugh, amma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan kungiyar Priorities USA da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat.
Amma, jama'ar Amirka sun nuna sun rabu a kan wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidar Fortne da Kavanaugh, suna nuna goyon baya ga na biyun.
Wani sabon zabe na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41% na masu amsa sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35% suka ce sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a shaidar, amma kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce hakan ya faru da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya yi wannan yunkurin, FBI ta fara binciken zargin da Ford ya yi da kuma na Deborah Ramirez, kamar yadda jaridar The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade sa'ad da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta yi ikirarin cewa dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aurarsa yayin da suke wajen wani biki lokacin da suke daliban Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo yana shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet domin gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya fara kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon abin da ya kawo wannan almara na fasaha shi ne Inrupt, kamfani da ke kan hanyar budewa ta Solids ta Berners Lee.
Tsarin Solid yana bawa masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su, da kuma wanda zai iya samun dama da kuma wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa dariya cewa manufar da ke bayan Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar dandamali ta Solid ta hanyar ba masu amfani damar ƙirƙirar nasu "keɓaɓɓen wurin adana bayanai" ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da ba a cika ba, takarda, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna nan a cikin burauzar yanar gizo, duk a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman na wurin adana bayanai na sirri shine cewa yana bawa mai amfani damar yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar wane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan damar "karfafa kai ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, matakai da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don sanya dandalin Solid a hannun kowa.
Kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners Lee, Bruce, wani dandalin tsaro da aka saya daga IBM, wasu masu ba da gudummawa da suka yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'umma na masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shiryen shirye-shirye.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere kere a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko an yarda su yi canje-canje masu ban mamaki, suna juya tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
"Ba ma neman izininsu".
A cikin wani rubutu a Medium da aka fitar a ranar Asabar, Berners Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo da ake kirkira bisa tsarin Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake fasalin Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT).
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai ƙarfi a cikin tattaunawar game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Ko da tare da Inrupt, Berners Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da zamanin Intanet na gaba", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Van: An Ba da Kyauta ga Limamin da Ya Sami Gicciye na Victoria a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
An girmama limamin Cocin Ingila guda ɗaya da ya karɓi Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na ɗaya a matsayin soja a ƙasarsa shekaru 100 bayan haka.
An ba wa Lieutenant Colonel Reverend Bernard Van lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, don kai hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana huɗu, kuma ba a taɓa saninsa ba cewa ya sami babban daraja a yaƙin da aka yi a ƙasar Britaniya.
A ranar Asabar ne aka bude wani abin tunawa da jikokinsa biyu, wanda aka yi tare da wani biki a Rasden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Van, ya ce "abin da ya fi muhimmanci" ne cewa an yi bikin cika shekaru 100 da aikin jaruntakar da kakansa ya yi da ya sa aka ba shi lambar yabo.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, in ji jaridar London Gazette, Laftanar Janar Van ya ja-goranci rukuninsa a Kogin Seine-Cet, a cikin hazo mai yawa, kuma yana fuskantar harsasai masu ƙarfi daga bindigogi da kuma bindigogi".
Daga baya, ya ruga zuwa layin gaba kuma da "ƙarfin hali" ya jagoranci layin gaba, kafin ya yi wa uku daga cikin rukunin hari da kansa da bindiga.
An kashe Lieutenant Colonel Van ta hanyar wani dan wasan Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, kusan wata daya kafin karshen yakin.
Michael Van, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan jaruntakar da kakansa ya yi "wani abu ne da na sani ba zan taɓa iya kaiwa ba, wani abu ne da ke sa ka ji darajarsa sosai".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Van, sun kuma kafa kambi bayan bikin, wanda ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ta jagoranci.
Michael Van ya ce "ya ji daɗi sosai ya halarci bikin" kuma ya daɗa cewa "taimakon mutane da yawa ya nuna ƙarfin hali na jarumi na gaskiya".
