Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Pallu na Indonesia ranar Juma'a, a cewar majiyoyin hukuma, yayin da ake sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Da aka katse sadarwa, ba a samu damar samun bayanai daga Donggala, wani yanki a arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Palo, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan da bala'in ya ɓarke.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke gefen bakin tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mazauna 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami suka addabi birnin, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40.
Donggala wata ƙaramar masarauta ce da ke da nisan fiye da mil 300 (180 miles) a kudu maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Wakilin masarautar, wani mataki na rarrabuwa a karkashin lardin, yana da yawan mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke tallafawa tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiya na Sulawesi, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma ana samunsa sosai a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938 wata guguwa ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin Rukunin Wuta na Yanayin Yanayin Yanayi a Tekun Fasifik kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na kwanan nan su ne:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14, inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen watan Mayu da farkon watan Afrilu.
An kashe daruruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 da ke da cibiya a kusa da garin Pandang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mendaui da ke kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai zurfin gaske ta afkawa yankin Pindi Jaya na Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, yayin da ta kawo wa duniya tunatarwa game da bala'in da girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisan gilla ta 2004 ta yi.
Ba a yi tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wani yanayi na wucin gadi.
