Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, an kama shi a kan zargin aikata laifin cin zarafin cikin gida, hana a kai karar cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma adawa da hukuma, a cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce, sa'ad da wata mata da ya san ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta kai rahoto game da laifuffukan da ake zarginsa da aikata su, sai ya ƙwace wayar daga hannunta.
An tsare Palin a gidan yarin Mat-Su, a kan belin da ya kai dala 500, kamar yadda tashar talabijin ta KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya ce "ba shi da laifi" lokacin da aka tambaye shi, kamar yadda cibiyar sadarwa ta ruwaito.
Palin yana fuskantar tuhuma kan laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin cewa za a iya yanke masa hukuncin daurin shekara guda a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin cin hanci da rashawa na aji A, wanda ke da hukuncin ɗaurin kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai Palin kotu ba.
A watan Disambar 2017 aka zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton harin.
An shigar da wannan shari'ar a Kotun Tsohon Sojoji ta Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016 ne aka tuhume shi da aikata laifukan tashin hankali na cikin gida, hana shigar da kara kan laifin tashin hankali na cikin gida, da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake cikin maye.
Abokinsa ya ce ya buge ta a fuska.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci zargi daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a shekarar 2016 lokacin da ta danganta halin zalunci na ɗanta da rikicewar damuwa na bayan-tashin hankali da aka haifar masa daga hidimarsa a Iraki.
Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia: Mutane daruruwan sun mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka rasa rayukansu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi da ke Indonesia ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasar mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta jawo tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
An katse wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afka kusa da tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Bidiyo na wannan bala'i ya bazu a shafukan sada zumunta.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin a bakin teku a garin Palo, lokacin da tsunami ya afkawa gabar teku.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa da ba a saba gani ba ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman a yanke wa Saifullo Saipoff hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba saboda wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
An ce Saipoff, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a hanyar keke a gefen West Side na Lower Manhattan, yana janye masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke da suka taru a hanyarsa a ranar 31 ga Oktoba.
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe "da gangan" kuma ya yi wa wasu mummunar rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar na niyyar yanke hukuncin kisa, da aka shigar a Kotun Kudancin New York.
An yi wa duka waɗannan laifuffuka hukuncin kisa, in ji takardar.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipow kan tuhumar da ta kunshi laifuka 22, wadanda suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai ga kungiyar masu aikata laifi, wata dabara da ake amfani da ita a lokuta da dama a cikin shari'ar masu gabatar da kara, da kuma laifuka guda daya na aikata mugunta da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma tunani sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna kwatanta yadda Saipov ya kai harin da "m, mai tsanani da kuma rashin mutunci".
"Saifullo Habibulayevich Saipov ya jawo wa iyalan da abokan Diego Enrique Angellini, Nicholas Cleaves, Ann-Lor Decade, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlich, Ernan Ferrucci, Ernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Panuko wahala, lahani da kuma asara", kamar yadda sanarwar ta bayyana.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shige tun lokacin da Kotun Kudancin New York ta yi shari'a a kan batun da ya shafi hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa mai laifin, Halind Barnes, hukuncin kisa na masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu, amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a kan wani shari'ar tarayya a New York, a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, waɗanda aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yakin Zamani shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg da kuma wasu a kan kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipoff, ɗan Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin tuba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa ya ji daɗin abin da ya yi, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Saipoff ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa an yi masa wahayi ne da bidiyo na Isis da ya gani a wayarsa, a cewar takardar tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a kafa tutar ISIS a dakinsa na asibiti, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan dukan laifuffuka 22 da aka yi masa a cikin takardar tuhumar.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin lauyoyin gwamnati na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun "yi takaici" da shawarar da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da wata damar samun 'yanci ba zai kara tsawaita raunin da abubuwan suka haifar ga duk wanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta riga ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi a yanke musu hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisa na Tory ya ce ya kamata a sanya Nijel Faratz a matsayin shugaban tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "karfafa rundunar soji" a yau a lokacin taron zanga-zangar taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Independence Party (UKIP) ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba" daga masu ra'ayin Turai, kamar yadda daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May ya ce ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Boone ya shaida wa masu zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa da a ce Farage ne ya kamata ya zama ministan Brexit, da Birtaniya ta "fita" a yanzu.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen sulhunta 'yan majalisarta masu rabuwa ya kara bayyana ne ta hanyar da 'yan Tories masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a EU suka halarci wani taro na daban na adawa da Brexit a garin.
Firayim Minista na kokarin kiyaye tsarin sulhu na Chequers a karkashin hari daga masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu goyon bayan EU da EU.
'Yan kawancen sun nace ta ci gaba da kokarinta na cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels, duk da rashin amincewarsu, kuma ta tilasta wa 'yan Euro-Skeptics da ma'aikatan jam'iyyar Labour su zabi tsakanin kunshin ta da "hargitsi".
Mista Bone ya ce a taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull yana son ya kori "shirin Checkers".
Ya ce ya kamata a ba Mr Farage lambar yabo kuma a ba shi damar yin shawarwari da Brussels.
"Da a ce mu ne muke shugabanci, da mun riga mun tafi", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit amma dole ne mu jefa shirin Checkers".
Da yake nuna rashin amincewarsa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya ba domin mu zama marasa ƙarfi.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu".
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da ikirarin cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya sauya tun bayan zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su zauna ba gaskiya bane".
'Yar majalisar dokokin Tories mai goyon bayan Brexit, Andrea Jenkins, ita ma tana wajen zanga-zangar, kuma ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina kawai cewa: Firayim Minista, ka saurari jama'a.
"Shirin Chequers ba shi da goyon bayan jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su amince da shi ba, ba shi da goyon bayan jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu da ke kan titi kuma a ƙarshe za su zabe mu.
"Ina roƙonku ku daina shirin Checkers kuma ku fara sauraro".
A cikin wani sako mai kaifi ga Mrs May, ya kara da cewa: "Shugabannin kasa suna yin aikinsu idan sun cika alkawuransu".
Farage ya ce a taron zanga-zangar dole ne 'yan siyasa su ji matsin lamba idan suna shirin cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Yanzu batun amincewa ne tsakanin mu - mutane - da kuma tsarin siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau mu ce musu, "ba za mu bari ku ku fita ba idan kun yi haka".
A cikin wata sanarwa ga taron masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku sanya 'yan siyasarmu masu saurin cin amanar Brexit su ji matsin.
"Muna kiran sojojin jama'ar kasar nan da suka ba mu nasara a kan Brexit kuma ba za mu taɓa yin shiru ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai cin gashin kanta, mai mulkin mallaka da alfahari".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan Remain sun yi zanga-zanga a Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'a biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
'Yan gwagwarmaya kaɗan ne suka yi ta yin taho da tutar Tories a bayan taron kungiyar a karshen mako.
Dan majalisa mai wakiltar jam'iyyar Labour, Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Conservatives ba'a saboda matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta a wani shirin jam'iyyar a lokacin da aka fara taron.
"Su ne mutanen da suke gaya mana cewa za su iya sa tsarin bayanai da dukkan kayan aikin fasaha da ake bukata don yarjejeniyar EU-Canada-style tare da wadatarwa, don iyakoki marasa shinge, don cinikayya kyauta ba tare da iyaka a Ireland ba", in ji shi.
"Wannan babban abin kunya ne.
Ba za a iya cewa Brexit mai kyau ba", in ji shi.
Warren na shirin yin la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa.
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa Sanata Democrat daga Massachusetts ta yi magana game da shirin ta na gaba a wani taro a garin Massachusetts na yamma a ranar Asabar.
Warren, wacce ke yawan sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, ta nemi a sake zabenta a watan Nuwamba, inda ta yi adawa da dan takarar jihar Jeff Dill, wanda ya jagoranci yakin neman zaben Trump a Massachusetts a 2016.
An yi hasashen cewa zai iya fafatawa da Trump a 2020.
Taron da ta yi a ranar Asabar da yamma shi ne karo na 36 da ta gana da masu jefa kuri'a ta amfani da gine-ginen garin tun lokacin da Trump ya fara aiki.
Wani da ke wajen taron ya tambaye ta ko tana son ta yi takarar shugabancin ƙasar.
Warren ta ce lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatin da ta lalace, kuma hakan na nufin cewa mace ce za ta kasance a kan mulki.
An kama shi saboda harbin da ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar dan wasan kwando na LSU Sims.
