'Yan sandan Baton Rouge sun sanar da kama Deaton Simpson, 20, a wani taron manema labarai da aka yi a karfe 11 na yamma, agogon yankin gabashin kasar.
Sun wallafa wani bidiyo na harbin a ranar Juma'a, suna neman taimako wajen gano mutumin da ke cikin bidiyon.
An harbe Sims mai shekara 20 har lahira a kusa da harabar jami'ar Southern a ranar Juma'a.
"Wade Sims ya sha wahala daga harbin bindiga a kan kansa, wanda ya kai ga mutuwarsa", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul a cikin kafofin watsa labarai a ranar Asabar, a cewar shafin yanar gizon 247sports.
Wade ya shiga don ya kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
An tuhumi Simpson kuma ya yarda cewa an same shi a wurin da yake da makami kuma ya yarda da cewa ya harbe Wade Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da ya yi tsayayya ba kuma ana tsare shi a ofishin 'yan sanda na yankin Baton Rouge ta Gabas.
Sims dan shekara uku mai tsayi 1.98, wanda ya girma a Baton Rouge ya buga wasanni 32, ya buga wasanni 10 a matsayin dan wasa a kakar wasa ta bara, yana ci gaba da minti 17.4, yana ci gaba da 5.6 da 2.9 a kowane wasa.
Grand Prix na Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya ci gaba da neman a lashe gasar cin kofin duniya, yayin da jagoran tawagarsa suka ba shi nasarar lashe Sebastian Fettel
Ya bayyana sarai tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya wuce Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar cewa umarnin Mercedes zai taka rawa a gasar.
A farkon, Bottas ya fara farawa sosai kuma ya kusan rataye Hamilton, yayin da ya kare matsayinsa a cikin juzu'i biyu na farko kuma ya kira Fettel don kai hari ga abokin aikinsa.
Fettel ya fara zuwa inda ake buga wasan kuma ya bar Hamilton ya yi tsere a ƙarshen tseren, wanda ya kamata ya zama abin ƙuduri.
Mercedes ta shiga cikin rami bayan zagaye ɗaya kuma ta fito bayan Fettel, amma Hamilton ya hau gaba bayan gwagwarmayar ƙafafun, wanda ya tilasta wa matukin Ferrari ya bar ciki ba tare da son rai ba saboda haɗarin yin laifi na biyu don kare kusurwa ta uku.
Max Firstappen ya fara daga karshe kuma ya kasance na bakwai a ƙarshen zagaye na farko a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
Daga nan sai ya kasance a gaba don yawancin tseren, yayin da yake riƙe da tayoyinsa don yin sauri da sauri kuma ya wuce Kimi Raikkonen a matsayi na huɗu.
Daga karshe ya shiga cikin rami a zagaye na 44, amma bai iya kara saurinsa ba a sauran zagaye takwas, yayin da Raikkonen ya zo na huɗu.
Rana ce mai wuya domin Valterri ya kasance mai ban mamaki a duk karshen mako kuma ya kasance mai kirki sosai wanda ya bar ni in wuce.
"Sai suka yi wasa da juna, kuma suka yi wasa da juna", in ji Hamilton.
Harshe na jiki ya kasance mara kyau.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi wa Sanata Diane Feinstein ba'a a wani taro a ranar Asabar saboda nacewarta cewa ba ta fitar da wasikar Christine Blazy Ford ba, wadda ta zargi dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da cin zarafin mata.
Da yake jawabi a wani taro a West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai ba, maimakon haka ya ce abin da ya faru a Majalisar Dattijai ya nuna cewa mutane "masu mugunta ne, kuma masu mugunta ne, kuma maƙaryaci".
"Abin da zai iya faruwa kuma wannan abu mai kyau da ke faruwa a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan a majalisar dattijai, inda kuke ganin fushi, kuna ganin mutane masu fushi da mugunta da ƙeta da kuma ƙarya", in ji shi.
"Idan ka ga labaran da suka zubo kuma suka ce, 'Oh, ban yi ba.
Ban yi ba".
Ka tuna da shi?
Diane Feinstein, kai ne ka yi wannan ɓarnar?
Ka tuna da amsar da ta ba ka cewa, "Ka leken asiri ne".
Oh, ba haka ba.
Ban leƙo asirin ba".
To, jira kaɗan.
"Idan muka leƙa... A'a, ba mu leƙa ba", ya kara da cewa, yana kwaikwayon sanata.
Feinstein ta karbi wasikar Ford da ke dauke da cikakkun bayanai game da zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh a watan Yuli, kuma an fitar da shi a watan Satumba - amma Feinstein ta musanta cewa ofishinta ne ya fitar da shi.
"Ban ɓoye zargin Dr. Ford ba, ban kuma leak labarin ba", in ji Feinstein ga kwamitin, kamar yadda jaridar Hill ta ruwaito.
"Ya tambaye ni in kiyaye shi a asirce, kuma na kiyaye shi a asirce kamar yadda ya tambaye ni".
Amma ƙin ta bai yi wa shugaban magana sosai ba, wanda ya yi sharhi a taron Asabar: "Zan gaya muku, yaren jikinta bai da kyau.
Wataƙila bai yi hakan ba, amma shi ne yare mafi muni da na taɓa gani".
A ci gaba da kare dan takarar kotun koli wanda wasu mata uku suka zargi da cin zarafin mata, shugaban ya nuna cewa 'yan Democrat suna amfani da zargin don cimma burinsu.
"Suna da niyyar dawo da mulki ta kowace hanya da ta dace.
Kuna ganin mugunta, rashin mutunci, ba su damu da wanda suke cutarwa ba, wanda dole ne su taka don samun iko da iko", in ji shugaban a cewar shafin labarai na Mediaite.
Dandy Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants, wannan shi ne wasan da ya fi kowacce wasa a duniya.
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga don Giants a kan Dandy
Dandy Stars ta yi fansa da rashin nasarar da ta sha a wasan da suka buga a ranar Juma'a a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants, inda ta ci wasan na 5-3 a Dandy a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun samu sauki da ci biyu da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Bouvier suka ci.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cooney sun kawo wasan ƙwallo kafin Dwyer ya dawo da jagorancin Giants.
François Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dandy sannan biyu daga Lucas Ludwald Nielsen suka tabbatar da nasarar tawagar.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da 'yan Adam Keefe suka sha kaye a gasar Elite League a kakar wasa, inda suka yi nasara da ci 2-1 a kan Dundee a Belfast ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu suka yi kara a kakar wasa, kuma Giants sun yi nasara a wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya buɗe ƙwallo a minti na huɗu a 3:35 tare da taimako daga Kendall McFaul, yayin da David Rutherford ya ba da taimako wanda ya ba da damar Bouvier ya ninka gaba minti huɗu daga baya.
A wani lokacin da aka fara wasa, Sullivan ya sake sa 'yan wasan kwallon kafa a wasan da ƙarfe 13:10 kafin Matt Marquard ya ba da taimako don daidaitawa daga Kauney da ƙarfe 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da jagorancin Giants a farkon rabin lokacin da ya zira kwallaye na biyu na dare a ƙarshen farkon.
An sake kafa tawagar 'yan wasan, kuma Bushar ya sake daidaitawa da kwallo mai nuna ƙarfi a 27:37.
Kowney da Charles Corcoran sun hada karfi don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba da damar Dandy a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen rabin lokaci kuma ya tabbatar da nasara tare da kwallaye na biyar na tawagarsa a tsakiyar kakar wasa ta ƙarshe.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su buga wasan gida da Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya rasa ransa don ya ceci daruruwan fasinjojin jirgin sama daga girgizar ƙasa
An yi wa wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia shelar jarumi bayan ya rasa ransa a kokarin tabbatar da jirgin sama da ke dauke da daruruwan fasinjoji ya tashi lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 ne suka mutu kuma da yawa ba a san inda suke ba sakamakon wata babbar girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske na ci gaba da addabar yankin kuma mutane da dama sun makale a cikin kango a garin Palo.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun gudu don ceton rayukansu, Anthony Gunawan Agung, mai shekara 21, ya ki barin matsayinsa a hasumiyar kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport da ke Palau.
Ya kasance a wurin don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air mai lamba 6321, wanda ke kan hanyar tashi a lokacin, zai iya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga hasumiyar sa'ad da ya yi zaton zai rushe.
Ya mutu daga baya a asibiti.
Kakakin kamfanin Air Navigation Indonesia, Johannes Siret, ya ce wannan matakin na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, kamar yadda ABC News ta Australia ta ruwaito.
Mun shirya wani helikofta daga Baliqpapan a Kalimantan don ya kai shi wani babban asibiti a wani gari.
Abin baƙin ciki, mun rasa shi a safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palau.
"Mun yi matukar bakin ciki da rasuwarsa", in ji shi.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na fargabar cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai iya kaiwa dubbai, yayin da hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasar ta ce ba a samun damar shiga garuruwan Donggala, Shigi da Butong.
"An yi imanin cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu, saboda gawarwaki da dama suna cikin kwari, kuma da yawa daga cikinsu ba mu iya kaiwa ba", in ji Soto Purguo Ngroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar.
Ruwa mai tsawon kafa 20 ya lalata Palu, wanda za a yi jana'izarsa a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo taimako da kayayyaki.
Risa Kuzuma, wata mahaifiyar 'yar shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News: "Kowane minti wani motar asibiti na kawo gawawwaki.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da wuya.
Ana fashi a dukan kantuna".
Jean Gelfant, shugaban kungiyar agaji ta Red Cross ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya gaya wa CNN: "Kungiyar agaji ta Indonesia tana aiki tuƙuru don ceton rayuka, amma ba mu san abin da za su samu a wurin ba.
Abin da ya faru ya riga ya zama bala'i, amma zai iya zama mafi muni".
Shugaban ƙasar Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa birnin Palu a ranar Lahadi, kuma ya gaya wa sojojin ƙasar: "Ina roƙonku ku yi aiki dare da rana don ku kammala dukan aikin da ya shafi kwashe mutane.
