Taron cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya yi ta'aziyya sosai, kuma yayin da har yanzu yaƙi bai ƙare ba, ɓarna tsakanin ƙasashen biyu na iya amfanar Beijing a dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya kaddamar da wata doka a farkon wannan shekarar, inda ya sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya faru a wannan makon, tare da sabon haraji kan abubuwa masu daraja dalar Amurka miliyan 200 (£ 150m), a zahiri haraji na rabin duk kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su Amurka daga China.
A duk lokacin da aka yi harbi, Beijing tana mayar da harbin a zahiri, kuma kwanan nan ta saka haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa ɗari a kan kayayyaki masu daraja dala miliyan 60.
China ta ƙuduri aniyar mayar da harin Amurka, kuma ba za a iya ganin babbar tattalin arzikin duniya ta biyu ta daina wannan aikin ba.
Domin ya samu nasarar sa Washington ta yi kasala, dole ne ya yi biyayya ga bukatunsu, amma yin sujada a fili a Amurka zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Amma, in har Beijing ta yi wasa da wasanta yadda ya kamata, masana sun ce matsin lamba na Amurka a cikin yakin cinikayya na iya zama mai kyau ga China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani mataki na siyasa da aka ɗauka da garaje a Washington ko kuma a Beijing zai iya sa yanayin ya rushe a tattalin arziki a kowanne cikin ƙasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura da al'amura a dā suka yarda", in ji Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike mai kula da nazarin Asiya a Cibiyar Sabon Tsaron Amirka, wata cibiyar tunani.
Syria ta "shirya" don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, in ji Ministan Harkokin Wajen
Syria ta yi ikirarin cewa a shirye take ta mayar da 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai, kuma ta yi kira ga taimakon sake gina kasar da ta yi ta fama da yakin shekaru bakwai (da dama).
Da yake jawabi ga babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al Mu'alim ya ce yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau halin da ake ciki a kasar ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da al'amuran al'ada.
Dukkanin sharuɗɗa sun cika don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira da kansu zuwa ƙasar da aka tilasta musu su bar saboda ta'addanci da matakan tattalin arziki na kai tsaye da ke shafar rayuwarsu ta yau da kullun da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar kasar tun bayan barkewar yakin a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke zaune a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako na jin kai.
Al Mu'alem ya ce gwamnatin Syria na maraba da taimakon da za a bayar don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da aka ba shi ba ko kuma taimakon da kasashen da suka goyi bayan tawayen suka bayar.
Turai ta yi nasara a gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe Kofin Rider na 2018, ta doke tawagar Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin wasan golf na Le Golf National, a wajen Paris a Faransa.
Yanzu haka, an ci wa tawagar Amurka nasara sau shida a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake zama ta farko, yayin da tawagar shugaban Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Tauraron tawagar Amurka Phil Mickelston, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya sosai a tsawon gasar, ya jefa harbinsa a cikin ruwa a kan rami na 16 na par-3, ya ba da nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan golf na Italiya, Molinari ya yi fice a duk wasanninsa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka yi 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sha kashi a 5&4 daga dan wasan da ya fi kasa a rukunin Turai, Danish Thorbjorn Olsen.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a duniya, ya ci 2 da 1 a kan Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya buga wasansa na karshe a gasar Ryder.
Tsohon dan wasan Spain mai lashe gasar Ryder Cup takwas, Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara a gasar da maki 25.5.
"A al'ada ba na kuka, amma a yau ba zan iya kame kaina ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki da muka dawo da kofin.
Dukkanin abu ne na kungiyar kuma ina farin cikin cewa na iya taimakawa", in ji Garcia cikin farin ciki bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da kyautar ga dan kasarsa John Rum, wanda ya doke dan wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods 2&1 a wasan daya-daya a ranar Lahadi.
"Ina alfahari sosai da na doke Tiger Woods, na girma ina sha'awar wannan mutumin", in ji Ram, mai shekara 23.
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa, kuma yanzu yana da tarihin nasara a gasar Ryder Cup 13-21-3.
Wannan shi ne ƙididdiga mai ban mamaki ga ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan da suka taɓa cin kofin duniya 14 da Jack Nicklaus ya ci.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi ta gwagwarmaya ta mako-mako don samun burin, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Fino, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf a matakin da ya fi na kowacce a gasar.
Shugaban Amurka Jim Farik ya yi magana bayan rashin nasarar tawagarsa, "Ina alfahari da wadannan yara, sun yi yaƙi.
A wasu lokatai a safiyar yau mun matsa wa Turai sosai.
Mun yi kokawa sosai.
Na gode da Thomas.
Shi babban shugaba ne.
Kuma dukan 'yan wasansa 12 sun yi wasa mai kyau.
Za mu sake kafawa, kuma in yi aiki da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin gasar Ryder Cup, kuma mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan yara 12 kuma ina alfahari da zama shugabansu.
Dole ne mu yarda da hakan.
Sun fi mu kyau".
Bayani game da jan ruwa: Abubuwan da ke tattare da shi suna raguwa a lardunan Pinellas, Manati da Sarasota
Wani sabon bayani daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa, a wasu wurare a yankin Tampa Bay, ruwan Red Tide yana raguwa sosai.
A cewar FWC, an lura da yanayin tabo mara kyau a yankunan lardunan Pinellas, Manati, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Wani yanki na Red Tide ya kai kusan mil 130 na gabar teku daga lardin Pinellas da ke arewa zuwa lardin Lee da ke kudu.
An gano tabo a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Tide a lardin Pasco.
An samu matsakaitan taro a bakin teku da kuma bakin teku a lardin Pinellas a makon da ya gabata, an samu low zuwa high a bakin teku a lardin Hillsborough, low zuwa high a lardin Manatee, low zuwa high a bakin teku ko kuma a bakin teku a lardin Sarasota, low zuwa matsakaitan taro a lardin Charlotte, low zuwa high a bakin teku ko kuma bakin teku a lardin Lee, da kuma low a lardin Collier.
An ci gaba da samun cututtuka na numfashi a lardunan Pinellas, Manati, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu rahoton rashin lafiyar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
